'''Yenikənd''' ({{lang-hy|Նորշեն|translit=Norshen}}) (also '''Norşen''') is a village in the [[Khojavend Rayon]] of [[Azerbaijan]].  The village's name means "new village" in both [[Armenian language|Armenian]] and [[Azerbaijani language|Azerbaijani]].

